Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.09,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停在靜止衛星軌道上的\n亞古捷斯旗艦,沙達朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被引誘進入那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.76,0:01:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼那傢伙\n不,哈曼小姐想收攬我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.07,0:01:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她認為我是一流的新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.58,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我只想找莉娜回來\n那女人欺騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三話 燃燒的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,聽見了嗎?波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.80,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皮革,你的敵人是高達\n高達...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.36,0:02:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,高達是你應該打倒的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達的駕駛者是捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.51,0:02:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達...?捷度是我哥哥\n不對,捷度是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.21,0:02:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度是敵人...我該痛恨的敵人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快清醒阿,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定戰鬥的目標之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以現在就停,如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫入作業完畢\n只剩實戰測試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.65,0:03:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了,就先做到這裏吧\n要送她去醫務室休息嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我帶她去見哈曼大人\n現在就讓它恢復意識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太危險了,她身心都太累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是醫生,應該做什麼你知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是..\n快到地球了,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我迷路了..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.86,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是逃的是什麼課程阿?\n不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.26,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵達地球後你要加入社交界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.12,0:04:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女孩身體不好嗎?\n她又貧血了,好了,上課吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.12,0:04:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位真努力\n是啊,很努力阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們知道\n自己是為什麼而戰的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,莫迪,不可以偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有在認真思考事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長\Nㄡ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想聽聽你們正經的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是討厭出擊...可是我們\n就是找不出為何而戰阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不知道嗎?\n你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.36,0:05:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護地球算不算?\n我們是宇宙主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是\n可是地球是人類的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.62,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們有保護地球的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度這麼努力\n是為了救他妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒那動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼很簡單\n你們想活下去就得戰鬥,你們無法回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到地球之後\n我們可能離開亞加碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會挽留的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.84,0:05:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,我很忙,有事的話...\n等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.08,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你恨我吧\n你發燒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說正經的\n對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於我拉你上戰場\n莉娜才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.05,0:06:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我正努力想救她出來\n救了她之後,你們要一起離開嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼久以後的是我沒想過\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是必須維修ZZ高達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,你太操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.83,0:06:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度救出莉娜之後\n還是不會離開亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.33,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是那種有始有終的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他太認真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\n他能成為正式的駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會瞭解到他非做不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,艦長\n雖然捷度仍是單身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他並不是遲鈍的人\n他一旦做了,就會貫徹到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,救回莉娜之後\n他可能更穩重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔別再操心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,你是志願兵嗎?\n是,我是相信正義站在奧幹這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是\n不然這場戰爭根本打不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,你怎麼大駕光臨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了,古利明\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.34,0:07:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是卡碧尼MK2的駕駛員\n波蕾...新人類嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她一定會成為哈曼大人的得力助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你的船不會來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼這麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.63,0:07:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去地球的話\n亞古捷斯的防守就會變弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.79,0:08:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若以為必須派小的去\n那你就擔心太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯雖然令人擔心\n但還可以重建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是哈曼大人只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不見得是獨一無二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人很多,小心點總是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會在旁保護的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.13,0:08:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球之後\n我會介紹聯邦政府你是我的心腹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,這是我的光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心保護古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的目標果然是巴卡魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.47,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想直接闖入聯邦議會\n直接鎮壓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們太小看聯邦政府了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.70,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,卡拉巴來電,現在解讀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.29,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的間諜,許多以潛入巴卡魯\n聯邦議會的會議程序進行不順\
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.85,0:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定延長會議期間...\n巴卡魯等於被亞古捷斯鎮壓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼果然厲害\n她早就把一切都安排好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,吃飯的時間到了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位怎麼了?\n你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達維修的如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時可以出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.81,0:09:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙達朗呢?\n艦長果然厲害,事事都準備那麼周全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.10,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙拉朗是三艘中的某一艘\n可是...莉娜可能在沙達朗的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,前頭那一艘一定是沙達朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,發出警報,進入第一備戰狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.58,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全面索敵周圍空域,敵人可能躲在任何角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你想找莉娜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓敵人的船無法降落地球\n再慢慢尋找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.06,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要破壞敵人船隻的防護傘\n他們進入大氣層就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是降落地球\n救人的機會不是更大嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這麼慢吞吞\n一百年都救不到人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,我來支援你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.32,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜一定在兩艘護衛艦中的\n其中一艘裏頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度好嗎?捷度好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達最方便行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!\n什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.07,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達借我用一下\n在那之前你用ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太任性了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,拜託你\n這次就讓捷度照他想的去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.63,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...求求你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.47,0:10:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開ZZ高達出動就是了\n真是的  對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是捷度,Z高達出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人\n亞加瑪進入戰鬥空域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.02,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪出動了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.77,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,你去那裏?\n敵人來了,我去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能狠心殺他嗎?\n這是我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度是你的什麼人?\n捷度是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.85,0:11:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我,波蕾\n捷度,桑達是我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,去吧\n遵命!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.32,0:11:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(想不到催眠療法這麼順利\n只剩下精神系統的連動攻擊問題了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.96,0:11:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲沙隊出動!\n桑德拉號回轉180度,迎擊以亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要出動\n剩下的交給你指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,視情況而定\n衝入大氣層也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何有一陣騷動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,我們再從頭開始吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(哈曼也開始懷疑我了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.70,0:12:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(我再不有所表現的話\n連我都會有生命危險)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,我來阻止敵人的MS\n茲沙隊,只要想著如何擊毀亞加瑪就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.87,0:12:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(感覺到了,就在我身邊附近\n捷度.桑達)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯跟MS隊來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.32,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼,是波蕾嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還在當駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.99,0:13:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是沒問題了...\n剩下的就看她的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法出擊,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是害怕,我是無法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\n艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.89,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個傢伙不肯出擊\n這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人擅自開啟戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.44,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑什麼要我們小孩子\n去打仗送死呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為莉娜而戰不算是理由嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜就算是我們的同伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快點準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面的人還指使我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太討人厭了,比查!\n艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.41,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會像頭驢子一樣頑固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自私自利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.49,0:14:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜歡你這個人\n但是你說的有理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把女人小孩送上戰場\n我們是最差勁的大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.25,0:14:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來開百式\n至少我還知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼開動MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.31,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多拉傑先生...不行\n百式...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查?\n這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員技術差\nMS就發揮不出實力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太口是心非了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,露卡出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,高達MK2,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.83,0:14:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人MS接近中,機種是,茲沙\n高達隊出動的情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,Mk2都出動了\n百式也將出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查駕駛百式,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.15,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,你飛的太慢了\n比查,你來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來外面總比待在亞加瑪\n被人擊沉的好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,住手!\n你不認得我嗎?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達...不是應該ZZ高達追出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.37,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達裏頭的駕駛員是露卡嗎?\n很遺憾,是捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾是你在控制的嗎!什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲沙隊\n波蕾,追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(必須甩掉他,救出莉娜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.91,0:16:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離進入大氣層還有一分鐘\n各區域準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.99,0:16:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現敵人的MS,不...是MA!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!\n來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.65,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桑德拉在幹什麼?快進入大氣層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.51,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏,莉娜,告訴我\n哥哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜...在那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才是你呼喚我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.61,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各區收納完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.96,0:17:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪沒有追擊過來\n桑德拉將其壓制住了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明幹的不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.87,0:17:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開防護傘\N4, 3, 2, 1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.81,0:17:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩艘船進入大氣層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮呢?\n來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮台的人在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.99,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,比查\n剩下的由ZZ高達處理,你們去支援捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,你沒問題嗎?\n那麼亞加瑪交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.99,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上\n比查,去吧 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓敵人見識ZZ高達的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,盡量放馬過來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣賭一下運氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.05,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手..\n波蕾,你不想吃巧克力巴夫嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧克力巴夫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.41,0:18:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那甜蜜入口即化的感覺\n你忘記了嗎?波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,你在說什麼笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.46,0:18:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其一個人吃\n大家一起吃不是更好嗎?波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:19:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?\n波蕾,你總算是記起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.22,0:19:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達...\n捷度.桑達是我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.06,0:19:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(她好像被人催眠了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.85,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟下手槍\n跟哥哥一起走,去吃巴夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快被引力拉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.65,0:19:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你把波蕾弄成這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.26,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度\n還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亞加瑪的援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.93,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能停下來\n誰來幫我阻止!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,運氣好的話\n想辦法活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.68,0:20:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可怕,救我,捷度!\n波蕾,你認得我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.54,0:20:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我,幫我停下來阿!\n好,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.01,0:20:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?燒起來了\n哥哥,好可怕,燒起來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維持那個位置\n你會吧,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在我的背部\n知道嗎?要看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來很難穩定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?兩肩燃燒起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.10,0:20:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,切斷兩臂\n不然你我會一起死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.80,0:20:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,這機體不能這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.02,0:21:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想就這樣燒死嗎?\n嗯...我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.78,0:21:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穩定下來了\n可是莉娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.53,0:21:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十秒後進入大氣層\n全體人員請做好準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.55,0:21:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.39,0:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是真的引力嗎?\n我們掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.60,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球好大阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.51,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開防護傘\n到達極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.32,0:21:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,固定進入大氣層角度\n到達磨擦熱的承受極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.10,0:22:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開防護傘\n遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.55,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
